text: Priory Heath Division, Suffolk is an electoral division of Suffolk which returns one county councillor to Suffolk County Council. It is located in the South East Area of Ipswich and equates to Priory Heath Ward of Ipswich Borough Council. ==Councillors== The following councillors were elected since 2001. {| class="wikitable" |- !
